Package: PvalVis
Type: Package
Title: A quick and easy way of visualizing p-values for basic hypothesis tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Emanuel Sommer
Maintainer: Emanuel Sommer 
Description: The visualizations include the assumed density, the computed and the highlighted p-value. Currently the following underlying distributions of test statistic are available: Normal distributions, student-t distributions, F distributions and chi squared distributions.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
LazyData: true
Imports: ggplot2
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
